cu.explanation_en: Setting the physical log level to an invalid enum 'invalid_phy' will cause physical layer logging initialization to fail and impair radio frequency monitoring.

du.explanation_en: Setting the physical log level to an invalid enum 'invalid_phy' will cause physical layer logging initialization to fail and impair radio frequency monitoring.
du.explanation_zh: 將實體日誌級別設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid_phy'，會導致實體層日誌初始化失敗，並損害無線電頻率監控。
